						<div class="postbody">I was wondering, does this bit (bit #0 in $2001) actually cut the chroma from the composite signal, or does it just assume a monochrome display is used &amp; uses a different palette or something...
<br />
<br />I was wondering because as you might remember, I want to create a Doctor Who game that progresses through all the doctors, &amp; I might be able to make use of this on the first 2 doctors.  Also I'm to lazy to set this bit for myself to test it out.</div>

					
